# English only in code

Use **English** throughout the codebase: user-visible strings, error messages, comments, and doc comments. Do **not** use any other natural language (e.g. Persian, Arabic, French) in source files. If you add localization later, use a proper i18n layer (e.g. ARB / `gen-l10n`) instead of mixing languages in Dart.
